---
// AboutSection — "Our Story" editorial layout with pull quote
---

<section class="story" id="about">
  <div class="story-inner">
    <div class="story-media">
      <div class="media-main">
        <img src="/images/h2.jpeg" alt="Healthy Staffords — our Staffies raised at home" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="media-secondary">
        <img src="/images/h4.jpeg" alt="A Healthy Staffords puppy" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="media-badge">
        <span class="badge-top">Est.</span>
        <span class="badge-year">2014</span>
        <span class="badge-bottom">Family Breeder</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="story-copy">
      <span class="kicker">Our Story</span>
      <h2 class="story-title">
        Ten years of raising<br>
        Staffies the way they<br>
        <em>deserve</em> to be raised.
      </h2>

      <p class="story-lede">
        Healthy Staffords began as a single litter at our kitchen table and grew into a decade-long commitment to this remarkable breed. We are not a kennel. We are a family — and every pup we raise is a member of it until the day we hand them to yours.
      </p>

      <blockquote class="pull-quote">
        <span class="quote-mark">&ldquo;</span>
        <p>We never measure success in litters placed — we measure it in the families we stay in touch with, years after the puppy has gone home.</p>
        <footer>
          <span class="sig-line"></span>
          <span class="sig-name">The Healthy Staffords Family</span>
        </footer>
      </blockquote>

      <div class="story-pillars">
        <div class="pillar">
          <span class="pillar-num">01</span>
          <div>
            <h4>Raised in our living room</h4>
            <p>Socialized with children, visitors, and the everyday sounds of a busy household.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <span class="pillar-num">02</span>
          <div>
            <h4>Temperament-tested parents</h4>
            <p>Both sire and dam are chosen for gentle, confident temperaments — never for volume.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <span class="pillar-num">03</span>
          <div>
            <h4>A life after pickup</h4>
            <p>We stay available for questions, training advice, and photos long after the leash changes hands.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .story {
    background: var(--color-off-white);
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .story-inner {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* MEDIA */
  .story-media {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 560px;
  }

  .media-main {
    position: relative;
    width: 85%;
    height: 520px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(74, 43, 20, 0.18);
  }

  .media-main img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .media-secondary {
    position: absolute;
    right: -20px;
    bottom: 30px;
    width: 55%;
    height: 220px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 8px solid var(--color-off-white);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(74, 43, 20, 0.22);
  }

  .media-secondary img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .media-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -18px;
    left: -18px;
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(107, 63, 29, 0.35);
    transform: rotate(-8deg);
    z-index: 4;
  }

  .badge-top {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .badge-year {
    font-size: 2.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 0.1rem 0 0.15rem;
  }

  .badge-bottom {
    font-size: 0.64rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  /* COPY */
  .kicker {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-family);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 28px;
  }

  .kicker::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 50%;
    width: 20px;
    height: 1.5px;
    background: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .story-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.12;
    color: var(--color-gray-900);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .story-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .story-lede {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .pull-quote {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--color-cream);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-secondary);
    padding: 2rem 2rem 1.75rem 2.2rem;
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 0 14px 14px 0;
  }

  .quote-mark {
    position: absolute;
    top: -8px;
    left: 18px;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 4.5rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    opacity: 0.3;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .pull-quote p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.18rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-gray-900);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .pull-quote footer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .sig-line {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 30px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .sig-name {
    font-family: var(--font-family);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .story-pillars {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pillar {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: start;
    padding-bottom: 1.3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
  }

  .pillar:last-child { border-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; }

  .pillar-num {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    line-height: 1;
    padding-top: 0.15rem;
  }

  .pillar h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-family);
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-gray-900);
    margin: 0 0 0.3rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }

  .pillar p {
    font-size: 0.94rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .story { padding: 4rem 1.2rem; }
    .story-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .story-media { min-height: 420px; }
    .media-main { width: 90%; height: 380px; }
    .media-secondary { height: 180px; bottom: 20px; right: -10px; }
    .media-badge { width: 100px; height: 100px; top: -14px; left: -10px; }
    .badge-year { font-size: 1.7rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .media-main { width: 100%; height: 320px; }
    .media-secondary { display: none; }
    .pull-quote { padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem 1.25rem 1.5rem; }
    .pull-quote p { font-size: 1.05rem; }
  }
</style>
